title: Smart Cheddar and Beyond Meat® Meatballs with Blueberry BBQ Sauce and Roasted Veggies
description: Sweet and smoky blueberry BBQ sauce is the star of this meal. It smothers cheddar-studded Beyond Meat® meatballs in this 4-star dinner!

